## Cài đặt dự án

### 1. Clone source code

```bash
git clone https://github.com/your-username/your-repository.git
cd NextNestEcommerce
```

---

## Chạy Frontend

```bash
cd FE
npm install
npm run dev
```

Frontend chạy tại:

```txt
http://localhost:3000
```

Tạo file `.env.local` trong thư mục `FE`:

```env
NEXT_PUBLIC_BACKEND_URL=http://localhost:8000/api/v1
NEXT_PUBLIC_IMAGE_URL=http://localhost:8000
```

---

## Chạy Backend

```bash
cd BE
npm install
npm run start:dev
```

Backend chạy tại:

```txt
http://localhost:8000
```

Tạo file `.env` trong thư mục `BE`:

```env
PORT=8000
MONGODB_URI=your_mongodb_connection_string
JWT_SECRET=your_jwt_secret
JWT_EXPIRES_IN=1d
```

---

## Build production

### Frontend

```bash
cd FE
npm run build
npm start
```

### Backend

```bash
cd BE
npm run build
npm run start:prod
```

---

## API chính

### Auth

```txt
POST /api/v1/auth/register
POST /api/v1/auth/login
GET  /api/v1/auth/profile
```

### Products

```txt
GET    /api/v1/products
GET    /api/v1/products/:id
POST   /api/v1/products
PATCH  /api/v1/products/:id
DELETE /api/v1/products/:id
```

### Orders

```txt
GET  /api/v1/orders
POST /api/v1/orders
GET  /api/v1/orders/:id
```

### Vouchers

```txt
GET  /api/v1/vouchers
POST /api/v1/vouchers/apply
```

